<div id="review_949923359" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/949923359" />
    <a title="Jamie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/51089-jamie"><img alt="Jamie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1286573170p2/51089.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/949923359?book_show_action=true">May 27, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jamie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jamie" href="/user/show/51089-jamie">Jamie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/51089-jamie?shelf=the-dirty-south">the-dirty-south</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/51089-jamie?shelf=the-wild-west">the-wild-west</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer949923359" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16221345522288582084">Funny, charming, cute as a bug in a rug (who would appreciate that mangled expression more: Taylor, Turtle, or Estevan?), but ultimately, it didn’t pack much of a heavyweight punch. I do know if I ever get a kid, the miracle of Turtle is how I want it to happen. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


