<li class='cover' id='bookCover_7247'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7247.Barbara_Kingsolver_s_The_Poisonwood_Bible"><img alt="Barbara Kingsolver&#39;s The Poisonwood Bible: A Reader&#39;s Guide" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388710089l/7247._SX98_.jpg" />
